8.2,, 120,, Crime, Drama, Romance, Thriller,, Danny Boyle, Loveleen Tandan,, Dev Patel, Freida Pinto, Saurabh Shukla, Anil Kapoor,, A Mumbai teen who grew up in the slums, becomes a contestant on the Indian version of &#x22;Who Wants To Be A Millionaire?&#x22; He is arrested under suspicion of cheating, and while being interrogated, events from his life history are shown which explain why he knows the answers.